## Async Polling Pattern

Many Citedy tools are async. The standard pattern is:

```
1. Call async tool (e.g. `scout.x`, `ingest.create`, `shorts.generate`)
2. Poll companion tool (`scout.x/{run_id}`, `ingest.get`, `shorts.get`) every few seconds
3. Stop polling when response status is terminal and return result/errors to user
```

Let the user know the job has started and provide updates as they arrive.
